GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Growth Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:47 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of developed countries across the globe. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in growth stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. It focuses on factors such as geographic region, industry sectors, individual issues within industry sectors and stock valuation levels, rapid growth in revenues and earnings, and potential for above average capital appreciation to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance...
GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of developed countries across the globe. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in growth stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. It focuses on factors such as geographic region, industry sectors, individual issues within industry sectors and stock valuation levels, rapid growth in revenues and earnings, and potential for above average capital appreciation to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI AC World Index and the Lipper Global Large Cap Growth Fund Classification. It was formerly known as Gabelli Global Series Funds, Inc. - Gabelli Global Growth Fund. GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Growth Fund was formed on February 7, 1994 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


