GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Telecommunications Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:47 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Telecommunications Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Telecommunications Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. The fund is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. It primarily invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating in the telecommunications industry. It invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations including small, mid, and large-cap. The fund focuses on factors such as rapid growth in revenues and earnings, potential for above average capital appreciation, market price of the issuer’s securities, and its balance sheet characteristics and the perceived strength of ...
GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - The GAMCO Global Telecommunications Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. The fund is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. It primarily invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating in the telecommunications industry. It invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations including small, mid, and large-cap. The fund focuses on factors such as rapid growth in revenues and earnings, potential for above average capital appreciation, market price of the issuer’s securities, and its balance sheet characteristics and the perceived strength of its management to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI AC World Index and the MSCI AC World Telecommunication Services Index. The fund was formerly known as Gabelli Global Series Funds, Inc. - Gabelli Global Telecommunications Fund. GAMCO Global Series Funds, Inc. - GAMCO Global Telecommunications Fund was formed on November 1, 1993 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


