Coverage


March 25, 2013
How They Won It: Cravath Thwarts $3.5M Vivendi Investor Suit
Cravath Swaine & Moore LLP successfully rebutted the so-called fraud-on-the-market presumption in defeating a $3.5 million investor suit accusing Vivendi SA of alleged misstatements and stock price inflation, using rigorous direct examination of the plaintiffs' witnesses and an unconventionally academic closing argument.


